{
  "stem": "802.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That we pretended to smoke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We pretended to do all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were Don Quixote.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were-- we were all sorts of great heroes, despite the starvation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somehow, we remained children, even though we were not children anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK, there was something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In fact, in the beginning, when I was about 12, you know, this was the first year in the-- in the-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, girls and boys begin to flirt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We even did that under these awful conditions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, for people who are not there and who are not familiar with the conditions, it may sound as if things were not so bad.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they were unspeakable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Nonetheless, we pretended that-- that we're children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we're-- all of us were, you know, essentially adults, because the responsibilities that we had to carry were enormous.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As a matter of fact-- remind me again about the sewers, OK-- had it not been for me-- I was a child.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it just-- it was just a coincidence, not-- not because I was heroic or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had a friend in the Warsaw Ghetto whose father was a-- a foreman in a factory for Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "A German factory, rather.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this man-- [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Justyna ?] is my friend's name, or Justine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Her father liked me very much because he regarded me as being gentle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And his daughter was a little bit wilder, so he wanted-- you know, he thought that my influence was a very good one.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that served us very, very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because at one point in the Warsaw Ghetto, if you did not have a work permit, you could not live.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these were slave factories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these slave factories were established at a particular time.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
